title: Trap Awards 5th Year Special w/ DC Young Fly, Karlous Miller, Chico Bean and Clayton English
itunes:title: Trap Awards 5th Year Special w/ DC Young Fly, Karlous Miller, Chico Bean and Clayton English
description:
The whole crew is back together! Karlous, DC, Chico, Clayton and the Pour Minds girls post up in the trap to give out some awards. Some of the awards are fan-nominated and chosen - others we just made up. This is one of the funniest episodes the trap has every seen and it makes sense cuz all the funny people are in the building.


The guys take a look back at some of the funniest moments over the last five years while making all new moments! This is the coldest podcast!


#85southshow #5yearanniversary
